Impuzu z'ibiro akenshi ziba ari ikoti n'ikivunga canke tailleur, kandi abantu bakorana bahabwa izina ry'umuryango canke izina ry'akazi.
Ubucuti buri mu kibanza c'akazi ni co kintu gihambaye, kubera ko bushimika ku gikorwa c'umugwi aho gushima ivyo umuntu aranguye.
Abakozi kenshi bategerezwa kuronka uruhusha rw'abakuru babo ku ngingo zose bafata, kandi bitezwe ko bakurikiza ubuyobozi batagira ico babaza.
